rs have been anncounced!</a>\r\n\r\nWhat choices will our audience make? How will their actions influence the game? You decide. <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/thekeepstudios?ty=h\">Help</a> to guide our game through a tulgey wood of conjecture.','Level Up Your Avatar!','','inherit','closed','closed','','175-revision-v1','','','2015-10-03 17:07:57','2015-10-03 17:07:57','',175,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2015/10/03/175-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(178,6,'2015-10-03 17:11:03','2015-10-03 17:11:03','<a href=\"http://thekeepstudios.com/the-keep-studios/tksp1-audience-xp/\">Twitch audience avatars have been announced!</a>\r\n\r\nWhat choices will our audience make? How will their actions influence the game? You decide. <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/thekeepstudios?ty=h\">Help</a> to guide our game through a tulgey wood of conjecture.','Level Up Your Avatar!','','inherit','closed','closed','','175-revision-v1','','','2015-10-03 17:11:03','2015-10-03 17:11:03','',175,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2015/10/03/175-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(179,6,'2015-10-03 17:16:34','2015-10-03 17:16:34','','Auto Draft','','publish','closed','closed','','auto-draft-4','','','2015-10-03 19:14:20','2015-10-03 19:14:20','',0,'http://thekeepstudios.com/?post_type=nectar_slider&#038;p=179',0,'nectar_slider','',0),(180,6,'2015-10-03 19:12:38','2015-10-03 19:12:38','','neonland','','inherit','open','closed','','neonland','','','2015-10-03 19:12:38','2015-10-03 19:12:38','',0,'http://thekeepstudios.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/neonland.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(181,3,'2015-10-03 21:14:16','2015-10-03 21:14:16','[vc_row type=\"in_container\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\"][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"Lady of Music; Change Queen; Bards\' Muse\"]Despia[/heading][vc_column_text]The Goddess of creativity and joyous change; Despia\'s abilities center around the ability to change the world in ways both large and small.\r\n\r\nShe is awakened by changes made in the world, and is known to have been especially kind to those who work to make positive change in the world, and so is also known to be a giver of small gifts and presents.\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"Gains 1XP per Dollar Donated\"][fancy-ul icon_type=\"standard_dash\" color=\"Accent-Color\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Level 0: 0XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Change one minor thing about the player characters.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 1: 10XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Make one minor change about the world.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 2: 50XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Make one major change the world.</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 3: 110XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><i>Make one major change to <strong>each</strong> of the characters.</i></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 4: 190XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\"CHALLENGE ACCEPTED\" TKS Will match all donations made to this point, and donate it to Extra Life on behalf of Critical Role.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 5: 290XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Gives away a Promotional Pack which will include a DCC rulebook signed by the GM with an insert signed by the players.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 6: 410XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 7: 550XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 8: 710XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 9: 890XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"The Watcher; Applause Maker; Fear Banisher\"]Grandiok[/heading][vc_column_text]The great narrator god, Grandiok revels in the fantastic and is a master of spectacle.\r\n\r\nHis powers will embolden the cast, granting them the ability to act out in new and different ways, and occasionally gift them with wonderous new powers.[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"Gains 1XP per Consecutive Viewer\"][fancy-ul icon_type=\"standard_dash\" color=\"Accent-Color\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Level 0: 0XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We will play our game live!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 1: 10XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We will find a fourth player</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 2: 50XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Keeper will dress up in costume for the next game</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 3: 110XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ability <em>???</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 4: 190XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ability<em> <em><em><em>???</em></em></em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 5: 290XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ability<em> <em><em>???</em></em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 6: 410XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 7: 550XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Keeper\'s costume will be in drag</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 8: 710XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 9: 890XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/3\"][heading subtitle=\"The Giver; Provider; Art Father; Purse Master\"]Mokdo\'ey[/heading][vc_column_text]Grandfather Mokdo\'ey, loved by artists in all lands that he is know.\r\n\r\nHe provides to those who create, and watches on lovingly but quietly, all while repairing stages, handing lights, preparing food and providing succor after shows and events.\r\n\r\nHis abilities surround supporting the other gods, allowing them to work further, longer and more often. Without his support the other gods would be be unable to rouse to their greatest of feats.[/vc_column_text][vc_text_separator title=\"Gains 1XP per Patreon Subscriber\"][fancy-ul icon_type=\"standard_dash\" color=\"Accent-Color\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Level 0: 0XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We will release the previous games as audio podcasts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 1: 10XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We will air a second pre recorded episode</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 2: 50XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We will play the second episode live</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 3: 110XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We will record an episode once a month</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 4: 190XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>That episode will be aired live!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 5: 290XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mokdo\'ey will double Despia\'s donation to Extra Life</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 6: 410XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>We will use the patreon money to create a regular programming schedule.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 7: 550XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability ???</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 8: 710XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 9: 890XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Level 10: 1090XP\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Ability <em>???</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/fancy-ul][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"in_container\" scene_position=\"center\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\"][vc_column column_padding=\"no-extra-padding\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" background_hover_color_opacity=\"1\" width=\"1/1\"][vc_column_text]This progression is in flux and may change up until the show begins, and mystery unlocks will be revealed as they are approached.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]','The Keep Studios Presents #1: Audience Character Advancement','','inherit','closed','closed','','143-revision-v1','','','2015-10-03 21:14:16','2015-10-03 21:14:16','',143,'http://thekeepstudios.com/2015/10/03/143-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
